| cntrycode | numcust | totacctbal |
+-----------+---------+------------+
| 13        |       2 |   14417.34 |
| 17        |       3 |   26404.69 |
| 18        |       3 |   20916.98 |
| 23        |       2 |   18148.87 |
| 29        |       2 |   17195.08 |
| 30        |       4 |   29033.55 |
| 31        |       1 |    9331.13 |
